{"tid":1940771,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"lunch食咩飯就知你係個點既人","createTime":"2020-03-24T03:48:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T09:47:33.000Z","uid":12458,"like":11,"dislike":59,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"38585982c9f16a3d95116f4738fad1322bfda415","tid":1940771,"uid":12458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T03:48:03.000Z","msg":"乾炒牛河-完全唔理會健康既肥西 平時黑人憎果類<br />\n蒸魚-呀叔 講親野都一定加會屌你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n盅飯飯-以為自己好幽默既人 多數係自私精<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n椒鹽乜乜飯-小朋友<br />\n燒味-食肉獸 基本乜都放得入口既垃圾焚化爐<br />\n沙律-港女 以為食沙律可以減肥 但又落沙律醬/汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多數睇錢睇到好重 但對屋企人好好<br />\n老麥/KFC-廢人 可以不用多提<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咖喱類-份人隨和 無乜所謂 但多數係悶蛋黎<br />\n湯麵類-天生唔肥又瘦但又成日話自己好肥果啲女士 天生有少少自卑 但份人要求高既<br />\n麵包-窮撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他-垃圾"},{"pid":"f0811a28b3f6516d1ca1803b08bacdfe1918558b","tid":1940771,"uid":315852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T03:48:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c72dd28b9a09e5cf1fd94bf1bb88bbfc729a5de9","tid":1940771,"uid":10895,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T03:48:56.000Z","msg":"鮑姐&mdash;&mdash;垃圾"},{"pid":"7fa153fc8438e22c66b19ee2b6e1e380aec82f4a","tid":1940771,"uid":174432,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T03:49:19.000Z","msg":"食鮑姐係咩人？"},{"pid":"147929263dfbe3f9dcd0515bee3749d2e6234604","tid":1940771,"uid":63313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T03:49:23.000Z","msg":"食鮑姐"},{"pid":"50b198a27befbe59a4ac4305ac373ecdb8bc42c0","tid":1940771,"uid":104811,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T03:49:26.000Z","msg":"咁食